= Section IDs

Section IDs allow you to create anchor points and cross-references.

== Basic Section ID

[#my-section]
== Section with ID

This section has an ID that can be referenced.

== Section ID Examples

[#introduction]
== Introduction

Introduction content here.

[#main-content]
== Main Content

Main content here.

[#conclusion]
== Conclusion

Conclusion content here.

== Linking to Section IDs

See <<introduction>> for the introduction.

Check <<main-content>> for details.

Refer to <<conclusion>> for the conclusion.

== Section IDs with Attributes

[#custom-section, role=important]
== Custom Section

This section has an ID and a role attribute.

== Section IDs in Nested Sections

[#chapter-one]
== Chapter One

[#section-one]
=== Section One

[#subsection-one]
==== Subsection One

